                    <span>I bought this along with about everything else available for the PMP.  The biggest problem I had with the book was the test.  They were invalid, too difficult.  I finaly took the advice of my PMP frineds, focused on Rita's Books and Practice test and passes very easily.  One reason I decided to go back and comment here was that before I took the PMP I let this lady's practice test blow my confidence.  Again, too hard.  If searching for PMP material, stay w/RMC. . .</span>
                  
              
